        caption: [Partial Feedback Edge Set example with $K = 3$ and $L = 4$. Blue edges $\{v_0, v_2\}$, $\{v_2, v_3\}$, and $\{v_3, v_4\}$ form a satisfying edge set that hits every cycle of length at most 4.],
