  example-caption: [3-SAT with $m = #ksat_kc.source.instance.clauses.len()$ clauses, $n = #ksat_kc.source.instance.num_vars$ variables $arrow.r$ $k$-clique on $#ksat_kc.target.instance.graph.num_vertices$ vertices],
